I thought I knew mithai, but this box completely changed that 😋

Every single piece has something unexpected, whether it’s a hint of know flavours, a crunch of nuts, or a surprise layer of chocolate. It’s like they took classic mithai and gave it a whole new personality.

I’ve already eaten way more than I should have, but can you blame me? 😂 

If you’re looking for something different this Holi, this is it! 🌸🎨 

#holi #holi2025 #mithai #holigifts

Finding a highlighter that doesn’t look patchy or glittery is such a struggle. 

But I think I finally found the one ✨

The Halo Glow Illuminator by @insightcosmetic gives the most natural, dewy glow no chunky glitter, just that perfect lit-from-within look.

A little goes a long way, and I definitely added way more than I should have. 😂 I blended it out with a beauty blender later, so check out the second half of the video to see how it looks once it’s properly blended. Hope that helps!

#highlighters #makeupreviews #illuminatormakeup #glowglowing

Here’s how I finally stopped getting asked for my ID everywhere 🤦🏽turns out, I just had to change my makeup 🤷‍♀️

If you have a round face, I see so many people contouring the way everyone else does, but that can actually make your face look even smaller and less flattering.

I’ve found that this technique works best for a face shape like mine, so if yours is similar, try this next time in your makeup routine!

This tutorial is perfect for everyday use, but of course, you can go more extreme if you want to completely change your face shape.

That being said, the goal isn’t to change how you look, it’s to enhance and embrace the features you already have in the best way possible. 🫶🏽

Share this with a fellow baby face who needs this :,) 

#roundfacecontouring #facecontour #makeupcontouring #roundfacemakeup

Okay, be honest, do you put sunscreen on your face but completely forget about your body before leaving home? Because same. But I finally found something that makes it super easy 🙆‍♀️

This is the @mcaffeineofficial SPF 50 PA++++ Sunscreen Body Lotion, and I’ve been loving it.

It has a really nice raspberry scent, helps with tanning, brightens the skin, and keeps it super moisturized throughout the day. What I really like is that it’s not sticky or heavy, so it actually feels comfortable on the skin. A little bit goes a long way, so you don’t need to slather it on.

If you always forget body sunscreen like me, this might be a game-changer! 

PS: This has fragrance so if you’re sensitive to fragrances, keep that in mind. 

#mCaffeine #mCaffeineofficial #Newlaunch #Raspberry #BodyLotion #SPFBodyLotion

I never thought I’d have such a fancy KHICHDI in my life, but here it is! And I highly recommend watching this video till the end because every dish is so unique and different. 🤤

This was the craziest food experience I’ve ever had at @tresindmum. Most of the dishes were incredibly unique, blending Indian, South Indian, and Italian influences in such an unexpected way. I had to skip a couple of courses, but the majority were outstanding, and I honestly can’t wait to go back 💗😍

That being said, it’s definitely not for someone with a small appetite like mine. By the 5th or 6th course, I was already struggling, but the food was so good, I just had to keep going 😅 

#tresind #tresindmumbai #foodbossindia #coursemeals #foodporn

I’ve been using the @letshyphen All I Need Sunscreen for a week now, and I had to share my thoughts because it’s just that good! 

It works beautifully as a makeup base, keeps my skin super moisturized, and with SPF 50 PA ++++ it’s the perfect blend of skincare and sun protection. 

If you’re looking for a new sunscreen—or just starting out with one—this is such a great, beginner-friendly option. Highly recommend! ☀️✨ 

Check it out at hyphen.com
